cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.SY 

This paper is likely to belong to the sub-category of cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it proposes a novel deep reinforcement learning method. It may also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it deals with decision-making in complex environments. Additionally, since the method involves processing visual information, it could be categorized under cs.CV (Computer Vision). The use of TORCS racing car simulator suggests that it may also belong to cs.RO (Robotics) or cs.SY (Systems and Control).
